iption": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"The Amazon logo over a black background with orange lines\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oO5UJPWxRGnemSkYKJptONRieVI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67558532/acastro_190920_1777_amazon_0002.0.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Illustration by Alex Castro / The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"8NVy7p\">Time really does fly, doesn\u2019t it? It seems like only yesterday we were looking at Amazon\u2019s July sales event, and now we are once again heading for the company\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24244180/amazon-october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024\">fall Prime Day roundup of deals</a>. <a href=\"https://press.aboutamazon.com/2024/9/prime-big-deal-days-is-back-october-8-9-offering-prime-members-exclusive-access-to-millions-of-early-holiday-deals\">Amazon has announced</a> that its two-day sales event for Prime subscribers will take place starting at 12:01AM PT / 3:01AM ET on Tuesday, October 8", "id": 1175610, "language": null, "link": "https://www.theverge.com/21493780/amazon-prime-sign-up-day-deals-sale-price-free", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 359, "source_url": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "How to sign up for Amazon Prime ", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-09-19T07:00:00+00:00", "description": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"BMW i7 electric sedan\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8D-KJtG8DKsNeFYj2qty7Bn_Amg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73595559/236573_BMW_i7_xDrive60_ABassett_0019.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Photo by Abigail Bassett for The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"JtFbl4\">BMW o